00:27:19.240 --> 00:27:19.840
Claro.

00:27:37.280 --> 00:27:38.400
Olá Youyi.

00:27:50.560 --> 00:27:50.960
Olá?

00:27:51.360 --> 00:27:51.880
Olá?

00:27:52.080 --> 00:27:52.880
Shen Yifan,

00:27:52.960 --> 00:27:54.000
